# Conditional Statements

## if Statement

```java
if (condition) {
    // executed if true
}
```

## if-else Statement

```java
if (condition) {
    // if true
} else {
    // if false
}
```

## else-if Ladder

```java
if (condition1) {
    // code 1
} else if (condition2) {
    // code 2
} else {
    // code 3
}
```

## switch Statement

```java
switch (expression) {
    case value1:
        // code
        break;
    case value2:
        // code
        break;
    default:
        // code
}
```

## Ternary Operator

```java
variable = (condition) ? valueIfTrue : valueIfFalse;
```

